Each step needs to run in a new terminal/tab

Begin ROS
1. roscore

RVIZ
2. rviz

Map Server
3. rosrun map_server map_server mymap.yaml

Add map to RVIZ (in RVIZ)
	Add
	By Topic
	/map

Initial Pose
4. In RVIZ -> 2-D Pose Estimate (at top) (click & drag)
	Publishes /initialpose

5. Run steps 6-11 on wolverine: ssh odroid@wolverine, password odroid, alias:wolverine
Every other step is run on the Cerebro/ground computer

PX4Flow (ACM 0)
6. roslaunch px4flow px4flow.launch #alias: px4flow_launch

Roscopter (ACM 1)
7. rosrun roscopter roscopter_node.py --device=/dev/pixhawk --baudrate=115200 #alias: pixhawk_launch

Hokuyo Node (ACM 2)
8. roslaunch hokuyo_node dvz_hokuyo.launch #alias: hokuyo_launch


Odometry
9. roscd odometry/scripts
10. ./pub_odom.py

AMCL
11. roslaunch amcl dvz_amcl_test.launch
